title: Iron Maiden DISCOGRAPHY (demo, EP and BoxSet)
description:
Personal collection of Iron Maiden DISCOGRAPHY.


Here are EP, demo and BoxSet parts.
All info is collected from IM official website and from wikipedia.


All covers are in ID3 Tag. All covers are in sizes between 800px and 1500 I think.

Note:

These are ONLY official releases, except DEMO folder. There is no official release of demo records from IM except The Soundhouse Tapes.

IMHO, EPs, demos and BoxSets are NOT part of REAL discography.
BUT they are as always, valuable part of collection.



Quality of tracks is MP3, VBR,
between 225kbps and 320kbps, around 260kbps.



ENJOY and SEED!!!
